sql:

FROM title t, cast_info ci, movie_info_idx mi_idx
WHERE t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.kind_id  >  2 AND t.production_year  >  1973 AND ci.role_id  =  3
